Dessert Toast? Bougie Indomie? Chef Lennard Yeong ( @lennardy ) dishes out how to make his 'guilty pleasure snack' and what he's been doing at home during this Circuit Breaker.

They will be answering them in the comfort of their own home (because stay at home!) and sharing things you can try at home during this CB period.
